collectible.name: The Lost Gnomes Lamp
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description:
When new Scarcity residents got to the island, they started finding hints of a lost gnome civilization, but no sights of gnomes themselves. What happened to them?

This lamp should aid in looking for discoveries throughout the winter.

1 lamp will be airdropped to each current resident, with a small reserve left for new residents or awards. 7.5% of secondary sales go towards planting trees in the real world! Let's see how many we can plant in the new year.

~ Happy Solstice 2021! ~

features.text: PEYOTES are unique AI generated psychedelic portraits. There aren't explicit properties, every PEYOTE is as important as other ones... just pick your favorite.
If you own one or more PEYOTES, you can join TrybeDAO community.
If you own one or more PEYOTE you can join TrybeDAO community, activities, governance and rewards.

PEYOTES are 4000 unique AI generated psychedelic portraits.
There isn't any explicit property, because everyone in the Trybe has the same value and importance.
Anyway, there are a lot of implicit rarities, for example portraits of kids are pretty rares.
